OL,3,C#50,000 approved for study to explore
OL,4,Cfuture of 'eyesore' factory
OL,6,FFifty thousand pounds has been
OL,7,Fapproved for a study to explore future
OL,8,Fuses of a derelict factory.
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway Council will
OL,11,Fconsider regeneration options for the
OL,12,Fformer Interfloor factory in Heathall,
OL,13,FDumfries, with a future vision study
OL,14,Fand site appraisal.
OL,16,FThe Category B listed building has
OL,17,Fstood vacant for over ten years and
OL,18,Fwas declared ownerless last year. Its
OL,19,Fdecayed appearance has, the council
OL,20,Fsays, created a "poor first impression
OL,21,Fof the town".
