OL,3,C#50,000 approved for study to explore
OL,4,Cfuture of 'eyesore' factory
OL,6,FThe decision to conduct a study into
OL,7,Fthe complex's future is not a
OL,8,Fguarantee of development, but will
OL,9,Finstead provide a clearer idea of what
OL,10,Fcould be done at the site, with the
OL,11,Fhope of attracting investors.
OL,13,FCllr Stephen Thompson, the leader of
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Council, spoke
OL,15,Fto ITV Border about the planned survey.
