OL,3,C#50,000 approved for study to explore
OL,4,Cfuture of 'eyesore' factory
OL,6,FHe said: "From time to time we just
OL,7,Fneed that expertise to carry out the
OL,8,Fright type of a feasibility
OL,9,Finvestigation. And then once that's
OL,10,Fconcluded, we'll get a programme or a
OL,11,Fplan for redevelopment that will
OL,12,Fhopefully attract inward investment.
OL,14,F"I think the council's very well aware
OL,15,Fof the fact that this has been a site
OL,16,Fwhich has been a significant blight in
OL,17,Fthe community - a complete eyesore of
OL,18,Fdereliction, and we have decided to
OL,19,Ftake action."
