OL,3,C#50,000 approved for study to explore
OL,4,Cfuture of 'eyesore' factory
OL,6,FDespite the site being ownerless, the
OL,7,Fcouncil has stressed it does not plan
OL,8,Fto take on redevelopment itself, nor
OL,9,Fbecome the building's long-term owner.
OL,11,FOn this Cllr Katie Hagmann, Convener
OL,12,Fof Dumfries and Galloway Council, said
OL,13,Fthat "although it isn't a council-
OL,14,Fowned property, we can't just stand by
OL,15,Fand let this historic building
OL,16,Fcontinue to decay."
OL,18,FCurrently the King's and Lord
OL,19,FTreasurer's Remembrancer has authority
OL,20,Fover the former factory.
